reviews.review_text:
Information update Whoever is in charge of maintaining the database here can you update the information to reflect the show took place at the Seattle Center Arena, not Coliseum. They are two seperate buildings. When we originally circulated the digital transfer that is uploaded here we had the wrong venue information and just recently were made aware of it.

Thank You
- Hot! A cloudy AUD, but brilliant show!
